<pre><code>![画像の内容説明](https://dl.dropbox.com/u/464501/2013-01-14/piyo.jpg "piyopiyo")

![画像の内容説明][link_id]
[link_id]: https://dl.dropbox.com/u/464501/2013-01-14/piyo.jpg "piyo"
</code></pre>
]]></content>
